Package com.epoch.energyDiagrams

Classes for diagrams in which the Y-axis is energy, such as orbital energy diagrams and reaction coordinate diagrams.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CellsLine
    Represents a line connecting two energy diagram cells.
    DiagramCell
    A cell in an energy diagram.
    EDiagram
    A diagram in which the y-axis is energy.
    OED
    A diagram correlating the energies and occupancies of atomic and molecular orbitals.
    OEDCell
    A cell in an orbital energy diagram.
    Orbital
    An atomic or molecular orbital.
    RCD
    A diagram correlating the energies of starting materials, intermediates, transition states, and products in a reaction.
    RCDCell
    A cell in a reaction coordinate diagram.
    YAxisScale
    Represents the y-axis labels of an energy diagram.

Package com.epoch.energyDiagrams Description
